summary: A high level mage has been discovered near whiterun, he appears to be one of those psijic mages. he has some spells that i\'ve never seen before and has a cracking set of armour! i should probably kill him and raid his stuff, after-all, its not as useful to him as it is to me!
descriptionHtml:
this mod is a first mod by me. 
its a simple mod - it adds, 1 lvl 30 npc - near whiterun check screencaps. 
2 potions.
1 spell
new armour set.
